# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Trivy ignore file — PRE-EXISTING dependency debt allowlist
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# These are PRE-EXISTING vulnerabilities in the Next.js frontend (next@15.1.3),
# present in both apps/web/package-lock.json and frontend/package-lock.json.
# They predate and are unrelated to the Revenue Execution OS work; the lockfiles
# are byte-identical to `main`.
#
# Policy (decided 2026-06): the Trivy gate stays a HARD gate (exit-code 1) so
# any NEW CRITICAL/HIGH vulnerability blocks the build. The entries below are an
# explicit, reviewed allowlist of the known pre-existing Next.js findings only.
#
# Remediation is tracked separately: bump Next.js to >= 15.5.16 (or the 16.x
# line) in BOTH frontend/ and apps/web/, which clears every CVE/GHSA listed
# here. Once bumped, these entries stop matching and should be deleted.
#
# ⚠️ NOT all of these are "just DoS" — two are CRITICAL and warrant prompt
#    remediation independent of this allowlist:
#      - CVE-2025-29927  CRITICAL  Authorization bypass in Next.js middleware
#      - CVE-2025-55182  CRITICAL  React Server Components pre-auth RCE
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# CRITICAL — Authorization bypass in Next.js middleware (fixed: 15.2.3)
CVE-2025-29927
# CRITICAL — React Server Components pre-auth RCE via unsafe deserialization (fixed: 15.1.9)
CVE-2025-55182
# HIGH — Next.js denial of service (fixed: 15.1.8)
CVE-2025-49826
# HIGH — Middleware / proxy bypass in Pages Router apps (fixed: 15.5.16)
CVE-2026-44573
# HIGH — Server-side request forgery via WebSocket upgrades (fixed: 15.5.16)
CVE-2026-44578
# HIGH — Denial of service via connection exhaustion (fixed: 15.5.16)
CVE-2026-44579
# HIGH — Denial of service with Server Components (fixed: 15.x line)
GHSA-8h8q-6873-q5fj
# HIGH — HTTP request deserialization DoS with insecure React (fixed: 15.1.12)
GHSA-h25m-26qc-wcjf
# HIGH — Denial of service with Server Components (fixed: 15.1.10)
GHSA-mwv6-3258-q52c
# HIGH — Denial of service with Server Components (fixed: 15.5.15)
GHSA-q4gf-8mx6-v5v3
